        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/miami/scene_flamingo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 8127ceab-5e7c-4018-ab91-1afc1d8a51f8).Image",
        "Description": "47, we recieved a Contract from an Anonymous client to take care of some... annoyances of Sierra Knox.\r\rThe first Target is Albert Noah, a Kronstad employee trying to Blackmail the Company.\rThe Second Target is Brendon Fulton, personal bodyguard of Robert Knox. Show Robert Knox that he is not safe, scaring him into retirement.\rThe Third Target is an odd one out. Brigitte Carbot, Sierras rumored lover, needs to be dealt with. The client seems to be Sierras ex lover, hoping to replace her.",
